{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01WHMWrpLq4wC73QxAwt1B4k","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information I need:\n\n1. The StatefulSet was deployed with intentionally bad probe settings:\n   - `timeoutSeconds: 1` for both liveness and readiness probes\n   - `failureThreshold: 2` (very low)\n   - `initialDelaySeconds: 15` for liveness (too low) and `5` for readiness (very low)\n\n2. The probe.sh script has `sleep 2` which immediately exceeds the 1s timeout.\n\n3. The secret IS correctly mapped - `health-user-password` secret key `password` is mounted at path `health-password`, so the file is at `/etc/health/health-password`. That's correct.\n4. The original StatefulSet had much more reasonable probe settings with `timeoutSeconds: 5`, higher failure thresholds (10 for liveness, 6 for readiness), and longer initial delays (120 for liveness, 15 for readiness).\n\nThe fix is straightforward: I need to remove the `sleep 2` from the probe script and restore the timeout and failure threshold values to reasonable levels. on fixing the probe settings first. The `sleep 2` in the script is probably the intentional bug, but I also need to increase the timeout since mongosh itself can take several seconds to connect, especially on first run. So I should remove that sleep command and bump the timeout to at least 5 seconds to give mongosh enough time to establish a connection.\n\nMy plan is to remove the sleep from the probe script, set reasonable timeout and failure thresholds for both readiness and liveness probes, and give the liveness probe a longer initial delay so MongoDB has time to initialize the replica set. I also need to verify the replica set is actually initialized and that the health-user account exists in MongoDB.\n\nLet me start by executing into one of the pods to check the MongoDB status directly.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2952,"cache_read_input_tokens":32310,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2952},"output_tokens":29,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5c4fbd6d-a34b-4d9a-ad8b-c0beb9d2fd08","uuid":"70cca18c-d4dc-490a-92fc-258b7dcdc285","request_id":"req_011CcRGquupskSg5wv4AJL1V"}
